

1): warrior2 script:  import base model as fbx, check animation, check bone direction, apply materials
2) delete allthe empties
3) Delete root and pose
4) Combine all meshes (select all of them in collection window and click crtl+j when cursos is in the viewport)
5) scale model down


6) auto rig pro -> smart -> get selected objects -> set markers
7) remove fingers (via limb options)
8) adjust bones
8) Set engine to Voxelized
9) select skin and bones and click on ARP -> skin -> Bind
10) Match to Rig
11) Set Pose -> Pick TPOSE
12) Apply Pose as Rest Pose

CAMERA (shift+c)